(1, 'Cơ sở', 'Cơ sở vật chất', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><u><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Learning Resources of a Large University</span></u></b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">KCB has its own library where the main text books for all of the courses taught are held.&nbsp; All of KCB&rsquo;s students on the University of Wales degree courses will have access to its vast &lsquo;Online Learning Resource&rsquo; facilities, which is considered to be one of the best in the UK. &nbsp;The computer labs at KCB have state of the art facilities, which include the latest computer hardware and software.</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><u><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Location &ndash; Central London</span></u></b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); " type="square">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">KCB&rsquo;s Campus in the UK is located in Holborn, which is in the heart of London in close proximity to the financial district of the City of London, renowned as one of the foremost financial centres of the world and the world famous shopping/entertainment district (the West End) of the City of London.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); " type="square">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Due to the Central location of KCB&rsquo;S campus, it is possible for the students to travel from all parts of London and its suburbs. This is a very important advantage for the students, given the possible requirement of finding a suitable accommodation in a particular area of London or one if its suburbs due to personal issues such as work, living with relatives and/ or friends, etc.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><u><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Campus Life</span></u></b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); " type="square">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Students at KCB have the opportunity to gain cross cultural experiences due to the Cosmopolitan nature of the City of London and the International nature of the students at KCB. Students from various countries from all the continents of the world as well as from the UK study at Kensington College of Business for various Courses. The atmosphere at the Campus is vibrant, providing opportunities to our students to express themselves in a range of ways.<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">International events and parties are regularly organised at KCB.<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">A range of events take place such as Tango and Salsa Dance Classes at KCB&rsquo;s campus in the evenings.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><u><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Other Facilities</span></u></b></span></span></div>\r\n<div align="left" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></div>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); " type="square">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">KCB has an eight story building of architectural merit in Central London (Holborn) as its Campus in the UK.<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Students at KCB enjoy the facilities and resources of a University in the UK and the resources are easily accessible by the students due to smaller number of students at KCB in comparison to a large University<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">There are three fully equipped computer labs which have high speed internet access available via the Server of the University of London<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Access to the online resources including the online library of the University of Wales, which is one of the most comprehensive in the UK is available for the students at KCB<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 17.27272605895996px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="line-height: 19.09090805053711px; ">KCB provides unlimited and free printing facilities for its students and therefore enabling them to utilise the online sources (especially available via the online libraries) to their maximum benefit.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">There is a well stocked lending Library within KCB&rsquo;s Campus providing access to all of the Core Text Books as well as additional Reading Materials for all of the Modules of different Courses taught at KCB.</span></span><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">KCB&rsquo;s campus has areas that are identified and allocated for recreational purposes of the students.</span></span><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left; line-height: 15.6pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">\r\n		<span style="font-size: small; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Canteen facilities offering a wide range of cuisines with subsidised prices are available within the Campus (allowing students to save on costs of eating out in Central London)</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(2, 'Giảng dạy/ Giảng viên', 'Đội ngũ giảng dạy', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b><u>Teaching / Faculties</u></b></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; "><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span></p>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); margin-top: 0cm; " type="square">\r\n	<li style="line-height: 17.27272605895996px; ">\r\n		<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; ">\r\n			<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">KCB has more than 15 years of experience in delivering Undergraduate level and Postgraduate level Courses of prominent British Universities such as Wales, Glamorgan, Hertfordshire, Portsmouth, Thames Valley and others.</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 15.454545021057129px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); margin-top: 0cm; " type="square">\r\n	<li style="line-height: 17.27272605895996px; ">\r\n		<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; ">\r\n			<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">The faculty members at KCB are highly competent with extensive academic and industrial experience. For example, Dr. Robert Mulligan who is the Module Leader at KCB for Strategy related modules has a Doctoral degree from one of the top University Business Schools in the UK. He has several years of industrial experience at international level and has held Director level positions at prominent organisations. He also has a comprehensive teaching and research experience over the past several years at leading Educational Institutions.<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="line-height: 17.27272605895996px; ">\r\n		<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; ">\r\n			<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">Guest speakers who are top consultants and practitioners at leading companies are regularly invited to deliver guest lecturers as well as speeches at KCB for the benefit of students. This allows students at KCB to gain valuable insights into both past and contemporary business practices in real life.<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="line-height: 17.27272605895996px; ">\r\n		<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; ">\r\n			<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">KCB prides itself in ensuring that a personal approach is taken towards teaching and learning. Therefore, the class sizes are deliberately kept small. The Principal of KCB personally takes an interest in ensuring that all of KCB&rsquo;s students are given individual attention by the lecturers. Regular feedback is provided to students on their progress from the point of view of assessment requirements. In addition to this, the personal tutorial system available at British Universities is also practised with great care at KCB.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="line-height: 17.27272605895996px; ">\r\n		<p class="area" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; ">\r\n			<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: Arial; ">In many cases the overall academic results achieved by the students on the degree programmes of various Universities at KCB have been superior to that of the overall academic results achieved by the students from the main campus of those universities.</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n');

